'''Aïcha Macky''' (8 Mutarama 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Nigeri|Nigeriya]] ndetse na sociologue .  Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa documentaire''[[:en:The_Fruitless_Tree|The Fruitless Tree]]''.<ref>http://www.andanafilms.com/catalogueFiche.php?idFiche=1289&req3=Aicha%20Macky</ref><ref>https://www.institutfrancais.com/en/work/the-fruitless-tree-arbre-sans-fruit-by-aicha-macky</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 8 Mutarama 1982. Igihe yari afite imyaka itanu, nyina yapfuye amaze kubyara<ref>https://www.institutfrancais.com/en/portrait/aicha-macky</ref>.  Yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Master I muri Audiovisual and Creative Documentary muri Institut de Formation aux Techniques de l'Information et de la Communication (Training Institute for Information and Communication Technologies: IFTIC) muri [[Nigeriya]] nyuma arangiza icyiciro cya kabiri cya Master II muri Sociology no muri Gukora Film documentaire muri Kaminuza ya Gaston Berger muri [[Senegali|Sénégal]] muri 2013.<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/aicha-macky/</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2011, Macky yerekanye bwa mbere bugufi ''Moi et ma maigreur'' yari yerekeranye n'imyumvire yoroheje y'abatuye [[Nigeriya]]<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=35192</ref>. Amaze gutsinda bwa mbere, yakoze bwa kabiri bugufi bwa ''Savoir faire le lit'', butera kwibaza ku makimbirane hagati y'ababyeyi n'abakobwa bo muri [[Nigeriya]] ku bijyanye n'uburere bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina. Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana filime ''L'Arbre sans imbuto'' yibanze ku rugamba rw’umugore ufite ubugumba, guhuza ubuzima bwe<ref>http://news.aniamey.com/h/107030.html</ref>.  Iyi filime yarashimiwe kandi yegukana ibihembo birenga 50 mu birori ku isi. Nyuma yaje kugurwa mbere numuyoboro wa NHK wu [[Buyapani]]<ref>https://www.lesahel.org/aicha-macky-laureate-au-fespaco-2021-avec-son-film-zinder-au-nom-de-letat-le-president-de-la-republique-a-pris-lengagement-de-mettre-un-milliard-de-francs-cfa-dans-le-cinema/</ref>.   Muri Kamena 2016, filime yatsindiye igihembo cya documentaire muri Afrika Movie Academy Awards (AMAA).<ref>https://www.actuniger.com/culture/17485-cinema-le-documentaire-zinder-d-aicha-macky-en-selection-officielle-de-la-27e-edition-du-fespaco.html</ref> 

Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umwarimu w'abarimu muri sinema igendanwa<ref>https://cinemasdafrique.asso.fr/realisateurs/aicha-macky/</ref>. Ayobora abakiri bato kuzamura ireme muri firime ngufi zivuga ku makimbirane nyayo mu bihugu bihana imbibi nka [[Nijeriya]], [[Libiya]], [[Kameruni]], [[Burukina Faso|Burkina]] Faso na [[Mali]]. Yatsindiye igihembo cya Alumni of Young African Leaders Initiative (YALI)<ref>https://www.fnac.com/ia4151248/Aicha-Macky</ref>, iyi ikaba ari gahunda y'Abanyamerika yatangijwe n'uwahoze ari perezida [[Barack Obama]] . Nyuma yaje guhabwa izina rya Ordre des Arts et des Lettres na minisitiri w’umuco wa Repubulika [[Ubufaransa|y’Ubufaransa]] kubera ubwitange yagize mu mibereho myiza y’abaturage ba [[Nigeriya]] na sinema<ref>https://africasacountry.com/author/aicha-macky</ref>. 

Macky yazamuwe mu ntera ya Knight of Academic Palms yo muri Repubulika ya [[Nigeriya]] hanyuma Knight of Arts. Yakoze kandi nka Ambasaderi-wagenwe na Oasis Niger incubator center ishinzwe kongerera ubushobozi abagore n’abakobwa. Hagati aho, ni umwe mu bagize komite mpuzamahanga ishinzwe umurage wa sinema nyafurika (CPCA)<ref>https://viedestar.com/aicha-elhadj-macky-fruit-de-larbre-africain-des-cineastes/</ref>. 

